Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海上的波涛声 比平时更加清晰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炫目的月光充满了天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那月光如此温暖地 拥抱着我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 若能尽情享受世界给我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.90,0:00:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.78,0:00:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 新威尼斯的秋天快要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里很快就要迎来寒冬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.29,0:00:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为爱丽丝先行成为正式领航员了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.50,0:00:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近的共同练习已经变成了与蓝华两个人的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.01,0:00:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华啊 开始变冷了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.17,0:01:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋天就要结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.03,0:01:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说 蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.26,0:01:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有两个人的共同练习
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.62,0:01:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是让人想起我们刚刚相识的情形呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然现在说完全不寂寞是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这是非常值得高兴的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.58,0:01:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们也不能输呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.73,0:01:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 一起为了成为正式领航员努力吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.92,0:01:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉…灯里…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.73,0:01:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不能再跟你一起共同练习了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要道歉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是一直努力着 梦想着这一天的到来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你晋级为正式领航员 蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢…我就知道灯里会这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有一件事想跟你说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:33.59,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(433,290)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那片 蔚蓝的大海与风…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 蓝华她晋级为正式领航员了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是个好消息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.19,0:04:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,称号是Rozen Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是蔷薇女王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定下来是那个了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.26,0:05:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晃一直都在烦恼这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候进行蓝华的晋级考试
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为蓝华不仅仅是要成为正式领航员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还要背负整个姬屋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过如果是蓝华的话一定不会有问题的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实呢 我还有一个好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桑塔·露琪亚附近要开一家姬屋的分店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(265,440)\fs20}Santa Lucia
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华要到那里担任分店长哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.76,0:05:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她说以后会变得很忙很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…不知道为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是件值得高兴的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华却哭得很伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:05:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.28,0:06:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天将对你进行正式领航员晋级考试
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在好紧张哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我睡不着…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我终于要面对晋级考试了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为实在紧张得睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以虽然是晚上 我还是出去练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 终于等到这一天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像也开始紧张了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长 谢谢你陪我出来练习
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.69,0:07:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静下来 就跟平时练习一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？那个声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.78,0:07:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.78,0:07:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬓子？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了 不见了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚从中学的同学会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一不小心就弄丢钱包了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明牢牢系在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 鬓子你这么晚在干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天…是我的正式领航员晋级考试
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.94,0:07:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本大爷最近也要进行晋级考试了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:08:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常了解鬓子你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晓先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 晓 我找到你的钱包了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？在哪找到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.54,0:08:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你掉在店里的洗手间了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…居然在那种怎么都不可能掉的地方掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭钱包 你给我去厕所睡觉吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.95,0:08:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点 晓 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？灯里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么晚还在练习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬓子啊 考试加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望天气不要变坏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:08:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得努力睡一觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.57,0:09:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 远方的天空很明亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午应该就放晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晋级考试…不如延期吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是个重要的日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新选一个天气好的日子再考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直等着这一天的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:10:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是艾莉西亚前辈决定给我考试的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以今天对于我来说 已经很重要了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.11,0:10:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过要是下午也一直下的话就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.27,0:11:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备工作都做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 请握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:51.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,热水袋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.72,0:11:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 真体贴的服务啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:12:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,座位和毯子都暖暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.87,0:12:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里到大运河之间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.33,0:12:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从任何一个地方都能遥望大钟楼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 雨过天晴之后我最推荐的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是这条小路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.67,0:12:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:13:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位是赛艇的选手先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.02,0:13:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的船桨都是自己做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的路要由自己来闯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不这样的话 就会留下遗憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明年我要夺冠！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凤尾舟要通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们终于到了大运河
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(515,440)\fs20}Canal Grande
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.09,0:13:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在新威尼斯的版图上画出一个倒S型的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大运河
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人您冷吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是横跨大运河的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里亚托桥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(427,440)\fs20}Ponte di Rialto
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也是水上通行之人与桥上眺望之人邂逅的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.23,0:13:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晓 她来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 伍迪 我们按计划行事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.76,0:13:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,hurray～ hurray～ 鬓子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}hurray～ hurray～ 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}加油啊 灯里！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是晓先生和伍迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚小姐也要加油～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快给我下来 小心掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凤尾舟要通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕阳西下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣马可广场和被称为Lagoon的泻湖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不断变换着色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.97,0:16:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像被温暖的颜色所环抱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在其中不断被治愈一样不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.41,0:16:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 操纵凤尾舟的技巧和导游词都很熟练了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还能感觉到灯里独特的个性
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…非常重要的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:26.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.19,0:16:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么再继续前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈 这条水路…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 平时是禁止新人进入的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 现在我们可以进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:16:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着水路尽头的 灯里的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.97,0:17:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很狭窄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比以前任何一条水路都要窄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到还有这样的水路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人不可思议地 感觉不到慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能感觉到 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.58,0:17:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们三人总是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一起练习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:17:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.15,0:18:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从船桨传达到指尖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.84,0:18:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深邃而静谧的 水的流动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与大家度过的那些日子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支撑着现在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有力地推动着我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凤尾舟要通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 这次的凤尾舟之旅太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠静而恬然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像凤尾舟与海水融合在了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 这是最后的路线
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.92,0:19:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里开始的路线由灯里你来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要成为怎样的正式领航员
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要由灯里自己来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要成为怎样的正式领航员吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事物即将有所转变之时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很不可思议呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.09,0:19:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都踏上了属于自己的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.46,0:19:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像相互催发着对方的变化一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连锁重叠起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切 从最初都已经被命运所决定一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈 就在前面了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.89,0:20:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我的终点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要成为的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.38,0:20:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是像祖母那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.76,0:20:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像艾莉西亚前辈这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像亚利亚公司一样的领航员
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从你来到AQUA
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:20:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的世界就翻开了新的一页
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.98,0:21:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些平凡的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都开始闪烁着迷人的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.61,0:21:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人施展了魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.10,0:21:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像温柔地环抱着AQUA的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,延伸到无尽远方的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.93,0:21:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天空与大海
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能与你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.34,0:21:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.34,0:21:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的海蓝宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.34,0:21:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(457,440)\fs20}Aquamarine
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.79,0:21:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蓝…宝石…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.65,0:21:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深邃的…蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.91,0:22:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你晋级成为正式领航员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.83,0:22:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.52,0:22:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.32,0:22:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.76,0:22:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了 我是正式领航员了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.79,0:22:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.34,0:22:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直一直…都憧憬着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.18,0:22:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从踏足这颗星球那一刻开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.07,0:22:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.37,0:22:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.27,0:22:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有件重要的事情要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.21,0:22:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.25,0:24:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断变换的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.78,0:24:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恬静温馨的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.36,0:24:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一个人的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.11,0:24:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 我将启程
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.45,0:24:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.71,0:24:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 崭新的开端…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.38,0:24:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 请握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
