Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:17.07,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}蒼い日差し浴びて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:21.47,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}風を切る君に
